`cybernetics` => to start the tui
`cybernetics dashboard --no-open` => to start the dashboard(web - ui)
`cybernetics dashboard` => to start the dashboard(web - ui) and open it in the browser
`cybernetics dashboard --no-open --port 8080` => to start the dashboard(web - ui) and open it in the browser on port 8080
`cybernetics gateway start` => to start the gateway
`cybernetics gateway stop` => to stop the gateway